He scolded me and tried to shame me. God bless if business is so good that you can treat your customers as you please. But despite paying over $1000 tonight we got up and left. And you know, this place and the bar itself and staff are good, however; when the managers/owners treat their repeat customers like scum I prefer to take my business elsewhere. Enjoy your handicapped bathroom all to yourself pal.
